:"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/274963/1557302684519-avatar/d4247287-5306-455d-8162-9b9411416870.png?x-oss-process=image/resize,m_fill,w_80,h_80","books_count":0,"public_books_count":0,"followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"created_at":"2019-02-25T14:48:11.000Z","updated_at":"2019-05-08T08:04:47.000Z","_serializer":"v2.user"},"format":"lake","body":"","body_draft":"","body_html":"<h3 id=\"8a887b45\">环境搭建</h3><p><br /></p><p>三端搭建教程：</p><p><a href=\"https://flutterchina.club/setup-windows\" target=\"_blank\">【Windows】</a> 、<a href=\"https://flutterchina.club/setup-macos\" target=\"_blank\">【MacOS】</a>、<a href=\"https://flutterchina.club/setup-linux\" target=\"_blank\">【Linux】</a></p><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"2c509530\">开发工具</h3><p><br /></p><p>1.<strong>编译器三选N</strong></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Android Studio下载：<a href=\"https://developer.android.google.cn/studio\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.android.google.cn/studio</a></li><li>Vscode下载：<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://code.visualstudio.com</a></li><li>Idea 安装与下载：<a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/3c87487e7121\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/3c87487e7121</a></li></ul><p><br /></p><p>2.<strong>dart自动生成Json实体类</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>idea插件：<a href=\"https://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/11460-json2dart\" target=\"_blank\">https://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/11460-json2dart</a></p><p><br /></p><p>网页版dart生成Json实体类：<a href=\"https://caijinglong.github.io/json2dart/index_ch.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://caijinglong.github.io/json2dart/index_ch.html</a></p><p><br /></p><p>3.<strong>Flutter框架库</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn\" target=\"_blank\">https://pub.flutter-io.cn</a></p><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"e51e79c6\">学习资料</h3><p><br /></p><p><strong>Flutter中文网</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://flutterchina.club\" target=\"_blank\">https://flutterchina.club</a></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>《Flutter实战》</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://book.flutterchina.club\" target=\"_blank\">https://book.flutterchina.club</a></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Flutter社区</strong></p><p><a href=\"http://www.flutter-io.cn\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.flutter-io.cn</a></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Flutter每周Widget</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLjxrf2q8roU23XGwz3Km7sQZFTdB996iG\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLjxrf2q8roU23XGwz3Km7sQZFTdB996iG</a></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>资源整合</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/f5a4a28e2888\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/f5a4a28e2888</a></p><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"6ac0dc43\">常用框架</h3><p><br /></p><ul><li>状态管理：<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/flutter_redux\" target=\"_blank\">flutter_redux</a>、 <a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/fish_redux#-readme-tab-\" target=\"_blank\">fish_redux</a>、<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/provide\" target=\"_blank\">provide</a>、<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/flutter_bloc\" target=\"_blank\">flutter_bloc</a></li><li>网络请求：<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/dio\" target=\"_blank\">dio</a></li><li>Json解析：<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/json_serializable\" target=\"_blank\">json_serializable</a>&amp;<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/json_annotation\" target=\"_blank\">json_annotation</a></li><li>本地存储：<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/sqflite\" target=\"_blank\">sqflite</a>、<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/shared_preferences\" target=\"_blank\">shared_preferences</a></li><li>异常统计：<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/flutter_bugly\" target=\"_blank\">flutter_bugly</a></li><li>图片缓存：<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/cached_network_image\" target=\"_blank\">cached_network_image</a></li></ul><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"0dfbe902\">常用命令</h3><p><br /></p><p>检查编译环境：</p><p><br /></p><pre data-lang=\"dart\"><code>flutter doctor</code></pre><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/274963/1557217108938-00ea20cc-b774-4002-b04d-566632664536.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=640&amp;originHeight=640&amp;originWidth=1000&amp;size=0&amp;status=done&amp;width=1000\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 1000px;\" /></p><p><strong>注意：检查编译环境时需要所有条件都达到才能正常编译，如有错误的地方，可以根据得到的提示信息解决问题。</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>项目编译(建议使用编译器自带的运行按钮)：</p><p><br /></p><pre data-lang=\"dart\"><code>flutter run</code></pre><p><br /></p><p>获取及升级最新依赖包：</p><p><br /></p><pre data-lang=\"dart\"><code>flutter packages get</code></pre><p><br /></p><p>升级Flutter sdk：</p><p><br /></p><pre data-lang=\"dart\"><code>flutter upgrade</code></pre><p><br /></p><p>打包apk：</p><p><br /></p><pre data-lang=\"dart\"><code>flutter build apk</code></pre><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"6b0a4cbd\">实用小tip</h3><p><br /></p><h4 id=\"d651af4c\">1.使用 <strong>stl、stf、sta</strong>分别创建 <strong>StatelessWidget、StatefulWidget及动画Widget</strong></h4><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/gif/274963/1557217108947-b8bb6fcd-e0f3-440f-bf33-0a7ae49977d0.gif#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=400&amp;originHeight=400&amp;originWidth=470&amp;size=0&amp;status=done&amp;width=470\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 470px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><h4 id=\"1190d8d0\">2.通过快捷键option+Enter(MacOs)或者Alt+Enter(Windows)来迅速导入包名（适用于Idea和Android Studio）：</h4><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/gif/274963/1557217108936-01c769da-49ca-4e48-a7ce-912373317e28.gif#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=400&amp;originHeight=400&amp;originWidth=470&amp;size=0&amp;status=done&amp;width=470\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 470px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>同时也可以通过这个快捷键进行其他操作，例如添加一个Widget、对Widget进行转换：</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/gif/274963/1557217108966-1535f984-f34f-4d06-a115-7dd451ab8c53.gif#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=400&amp;originHeight=400&amp;originWidth=470&amp;size=0&amp;status=done&amp;width=470\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 470px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"229b2a29\">生成apk二维码</h3><p><br /></p><p>下面举个例子，可以通过上传apk文件，然后将文件地址转换为二维码的方式来生成二维码：</p><p><br /></p><h4 id=\"cc1e64d1\">一、上传文件：</h4><p><br /></p><p>以我常用的腾讯云 <strong>对象存储</strong> 为例，需将apk上传至云服务器：</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/274963/1557217108955-84e2f1eb-83f0-4d36-a6db-946866efbc9b.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=400&amp;originHeight=400&amp;originWidth=1000&amp;size=0&amp;status=done&amp;width=1000\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 1000px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>上传成功后进入到详情页</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/274963/1557217108946-1bfd798c-04fc-4c90-b0a9-8b4bff445468.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=228&amp;originHeight=228&amp;originWidth=1000&amp;size=0&amp;status=done&amp;width=1000\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 1000px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>获取到文件的下载地址</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/274963/1557217108956-fc8f5cf7-8e38-4ce4-88b6-d78176d2e060.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=696&amp;originHeight=696&amp;originWidth=1000&amp;size=0&amp;status=done&amp;width=1000\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 1000px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><h4 id=\"39b27e37\">二、生成二维码</h4><p><br /></p><p>可以使用 <a href=\"https://cli.im/url\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>草料二维码</strong></a></p><p><br /></p><p>直接将网址生成二维码即可</p><p><br /></p><p>下面是生成的apk二维码：</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/274963/1557217108950-a72e16a9-76ce-443b-870c-d36aa31e778e.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=260&amp;originHeight=260&amp;originWidth=260&amp;size=0&amp;status=done&amp;width=260\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 260px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>说明：Android端的安装包应该放在公司的服务器，之后Android的应用内升级同样依赖于这个服务器完成。扫码下载的地址也应该是公司服务器内提供的地址。</strong></p>","body_lake":"<!doctype lake><h3 id=\"8a887b45\">环境搭建</h3><p><br /></p><p>三端搭建教程：</p><p><a href=\"https://flutterchina.club/setup-windows\" target=\"_blank\">【Windows】</a> 、<a href=\"https://flutterchina.club/setup-macos\" target=\"_blank\">【MacOS】</a>、<a href=\"https://flutterchina.club/setup-linux\" target=\"_blank\">【Linux】</a></p><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"2c509530\">开发工具</h3><p><br /></p><p>1.<strong>编译器三选N</strong></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Android Studio下载：<a href=\"https://developer.android.google.cn/studio\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.android.google.cn/studio</a></li><li>Vscode下载：<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://code.visualstudio.com</a></li><li>Idea 安装与下载：<a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/3c87487e7121\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/3c87487e7121</a></li></ul><p><br /></p><p>2.<strong>dart自动生成Json实体类</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>idea插件：<a href=\"https://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/11460-json2dart\" target=\"_blank\">https://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/11460-json2dart</a></p><p><br /></p><p>网页版dart生成Json实体类：<a href=\"https://caijinglong.github.io/json2dart/index_ch.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://caijinglong.github.io/json2dart/index_ch.html</a></p><p><br /></p><p>3.<strong>Flutter框架库</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn\" target=\"_blank\">https://pub.flutter-io.cn</a></p><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"e51e79c6\">学习资料</h3><p><br /></p><p><strong>Flutter中文网</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://flutterchina.club\" target=\"_blank\">https://flutterchina.club</a></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>《Flutter实战》</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://book.flutterchina.club\" target=\"_blank\">https://book.flutterchina.club</a></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Flutter社区</strong></p><p><a href=\"http://www.flutter-io.cn\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.flutter-io.cn</a></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Flutter每周Widget</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLjxrf2q8roU23XGwz3Km7sQZFTdB996iG\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLjxrf2q8roU23XGwz3Km7sQZFTdB996iG</a></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>资源整合</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/f5a4a28e2888\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/f5a4a28e2888</a></p><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"6ac0dc43\">常用框架</h3><p><br /></p><ul><li>状态管理：<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/flutter_redux\" target=\"_blank\">flutter_redux</a>、 <a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/fish_redux#-readme-tab-\" target=\"_blank\">fish_redux</a>、<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/provide\" target=\"_blank\">provide</a>、<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/flutter_bloc\" target=\"_blank\">flutter_bloc</a></li><li>网络请求：<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/dio\" target=\"_blank\">dio</a></li><li>Json解析：<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/json_serializable\" target=\"_blank\">json_serializable</a>&amp;<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/json_annotation\" target=\"_blank\">json_annotation</a></li><li>本地存储：<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/sqflite\" target=\"_blank\">sqflite</a>、<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/shared_preferences\" target=\"_blank\">shared_preferences</a></li><li>异常统计：<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/flutter_bugly\" target=\"_blank\">flutter_bugly</a></li><li>图片缓存：<a href=\"https://pub.flutter-io.cn/packages/cached_network_image\" target=\"_blank\">cached_network_image</a></li></ul><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"0dfbe902\">常用命令</h3><p><br /></p><p>检查编译环境：</p><p><br /></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22dart%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22flutter%20doctor%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22e192b943%22%7D\"></card><p><br /></p><p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2019%2Fpng%2F274963%2F1557217108938-00ea20cc-b774-4002-b04d-566632664536.png%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1000%2C%22originHeight%22%3A640%2C%22size%22%3A0%2C%22display%22%3A%22inline%22%2C%22align%22%3A%22left%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22width%22%3A1000%2C%22height%22%3A640%7D\"></card></